OL,3,CMan in court charged with manslaughter
OL,4,Csix years after woman took her life
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fwith manslaughter after a woman took
OL,8,Fher own life six years ago.
OL,10,FGillian Morand, 36, died in south-east
OL,11,FLondon in March 2020, and an inquest
OL,12,Fruled that her death was suicide, the
OL,13,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,15,FAllegations of domestic abuse that Ms
OL,16,FMorand had previously suffered then
OL,17,Fcame to light and Scotland Yard
OL,18,Flaunched an investigation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/2
