OL,3,CMan in court charged with manslaughter
OL,4,Csix years after woman took her life
OL,6,FSeyhan Assaf, 45, of Berwick Crescent,
OL,7,FSidcup, has been charged with
OL,8,Fmanslaughter and coercive or
OL,9,Fcontrolling behaviour.
OL,11,FAssaf appeared at Bromley Magistrates'
OL,12,FCourt on Saturday wearing a grey
OL,13,Fjumper and spoke to confirm his name,
OL,14,Fdate of birth and address.
OL,16,FHe was remanded into custody by Judge
OL,17,FVanessa Lloyd and told he will next
OL,18,Fappear at the Old Bailey on April 7.
